# InterviewVault frontend env vars
#
# WEB BUILDS (running in browser): leave these unset. The app uses Vite's
# /api proxy in dev, and Caddy/Vercel rewrite rules in prod.
#
# MOBILE BUILDS (Capacitor → iOS/Android): VITE_API_URL MUST be set to the
# full URL of your deployed backend, because mobile WebViews have no proxy.
# Copy this file to `.env.production` for mobile builds and fill in the URL.

VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-domain.com/api
